            <div>
            <h3>Kayaking</h3>
            <p>Glide across the crystal-blue waters of Moffat Bay as you kayak along quiet shorelines and hidden coves. Kayakers often spot seals, eagles, and other wildlife while enjoying calm waters and beautiful coastal scenery. Guided tours are available for beginners and seasoned paddlers alike.</p>
            </div>
