            <div>
            <h3>Whale Watching</h3>
            <p>The San Juan Islands are one of the world&#39;s premier whale-watching destinations. From Joviedsa Island, visitors can witness orcas, humpback whales, and porpoises in their natural habitat. Whether from a boat tour or a scenic lookout point, it&#39;s an unforgettable experience for nature lovers.</p>
            </div>
