            <h3>Scuba Diving</h3>
            <p>Beneath the waves of Moffat Bay lies a vibrant underwater world full of colorful marine life, kelp forests, and hidden rock formations. Clear waters make this island a favorite among divers, offering safe, exciting dive sites for both beginners and advanced explorers.</p>
